Double wow! I am officially on Getty Images, and it feels absolutely surreal! 🌠💫

A massive shoutout and heartfelt thanks to Monica Schipper for the 2021 capture and to Noam Galai for the 2023 shot on Getty!!!! 🙌 You both have immortalized these moments, and I am beyond grateful for your incredible talent! 📸💖
